{"tid":2339131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京簽新法 全家終身免刑責","createTime":"2020-12-24T11:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T20:13:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":339,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"26bec2630076135bd14383dd7b7c0e03dc261e5a","tid":2339131,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/4U422ROM5BGYJKGE7MH7YUP3ZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2F4U422ROM5BGYJKGE7MH7YUP3ZQ%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=37776dc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2F4U422ROM5BGYJKGE7MH7YUP3ZQ%2F&h=ef3d6bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/4U422ROM5BGYJKGE7MH7YUP3ZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n普京簽新法 全家終身免刑責<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/addlZOi4njbnjxvy22kpqRhjy5U=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7LL56PRDZHFVCHO4BK2RS7YEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaddlZOi4njbnjxvy22kpqRhjy5U%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7LL56PRDZHFVCHO4BK2RS7YEI.jpg&h=e81a3709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普京<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京前日簽署新法案，授予前總統離職後，全家可享終身豁免刑事起訴、搜查及拘捕權。早前成功修憲讓自己可以連任到2036年的普京，被指已着手準備下台後的安排。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳健康欠佳為卸任鋪路<br />\n<br />\n新法例生效前，俄國前總統的刑事豁免權僅限於任內的事情；新法則包含離職後的不當行為。雖然今後若是遭最高法院判定違反叛國等嚴重罪行，前總統仍可被褫奪終身豁免權，但條件是必須得聯邦委員會（上議院）絕大比數通過。普京不但在新法例訂明，總統卸任後可在聯邦委員會內享有終身議席，更容許在離職前安插最多30名親信入委員會，變相令該會難以達到剝奪前總統終身豁免權的門檻。<br />\n<br />\n68歲的普京已掌權20年，現時是第四個總統任期，之前礙於憲法規定連任不超過兩屆，他曾退居總理，其間仍被視為俄羅斯的「話事人」。今年武漢肺炎疫情肆虐下，莫斯科推動公投修憲，雖然沒有拿走連任的限制，卻把普京的四屆任期「歸零」，讓他可以在2024年再次參加大選。<br />\n<br />\n不過事情發展卻峯迴路轉，正當大家都以為普京會再做多兩屆至2036年，國會上月卻草擬新例，外界猜測這位政治強人或有意交棒，原因或是健康已大不如前，但其後克里姆林宮否認傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n2000年，普京入主克宮後簽發的第一道總統命令，正是給予前總統葉利欽刑事豁免權。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"fc1c93ce3652ea79f03b8739105757c94c8324d0","tid":2339131,"uid":15815,"like":172,"dislike":3,"score":169,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"都唔穩陣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳位畀自己仔女啦最好"},{"pid":"9b4ac66e692151c501abde9a29d42f2bf41bed9b","tid":2339131,"uid":340088,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"民事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94110b6121b75963603193994a67f1e85b2bf823","tid":2339131,"uid":29514,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"做佢個仔就好，強姦殺人都無事"},{"pid":"2e44e98bff926b6da6261d230941ee733b5792d6","tid":2339131,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8b3605ae27edf53ce3efacd9b1fcfac33f9cda","tid":2339131,"uid":211941,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"習大大又可以咁做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ea7129144ee61a9256116f4927087cd09b2b39","tid":2339131,"uid":29497,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"做完又做，永續"},{"pid":"f066fd15fdee54c842cdaa58a837a1fea11a9b16","tid":2339131,"uid":143241,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4d8b3605ae27edf53ce3efacd9b1fcfac33f9cda","tid":2339131,"uid":211941,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"習大大又可以咁做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse